title: SafeVixAI
abstract: >-
  AI-powered road safety PWA for IIT Madras Road Safety Hackathon 2026.
  Features emergency locator, AI chatbot, challan calculator, and road reporter.
  Three services: Next.js 15 frontend, FastAPI backend, FastAPI chatbot with 9-provider LLM fallback.
